{"type": "article", "id": 14960, "title": "水果检测器", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-16T07:29:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061354355wi6RrDcYXzlfZk8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个水果检测器，根据水果散发出的气味来判断新鲜程度和保质期。将它放进篮子里，并转动到该种水果的图案上，就可以进行检测了。水果的气体会顺着漏孔传上去，由传感器进行判断，如果发出蜂鸣声并亮灯，就说明接近保质期了。这个设计还是一个概念，但对于西瓜或菠萝等难以判断的食物是非常有用的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142335KgmlIoPVJCjUhDrz.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"743\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261423358PyA5vQb6hUzu1cw.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"743\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142336Wasp0QneHigvfJ7r.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142336WFSMoLHeGhya2cZp.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"553\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}